You can pack a summary of the code in a markdown file with repomix, with executing the following example command, that you have to adapt to the current project:

Pack the web client code
`npx repomix@latest ./web/src -o ./agent/code-packs/web.md`

Pack the server code
`npx repomix@latest ./server/src -o ./agent/code-packs/server.md`

Pack the mobile client code
`npx repomix@latest ./web/src -o ./agent/code-packs/web.md`
